Package com.iontrading.mkv.bulkentitlements

The classes in this package pose the core of the Bulk Entitlement Query API.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMkvBulkEntitlementRequest
    MkvBulkEntitlementRequest represents a request for a Bulk Entitlement Query.
    IMkvBulkEntitlementRequestListener
    IMkvBulkEntitlementRequestListener is the listener called by the Entitlement API for each result of a Bulk Entitlement Query.
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceCallback
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceCallback contains the callbacks for Resource stream events
    Applications should call the methods of IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceCallback whenever a new stream is created.
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceStream
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceStream is the stream of Resources that will be used by the Entitlement API to resolve any Bulk Query.
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceStreamFactory
    IMkvBulkEntitlementResourceStreamFactory is a factory of MkvBulkEntitlementResourceStream An proper implementation of this interface is required to perform Bulk Entitlement Queries to the Entitlement API.
    IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener
    IMkvByFeatureEntitlementReportListener is used to get notifications about ByFeature Report completion and execution errors.
    IMkvByFeatureReport
    A wrapper object for the ByFeature Report.
    IMkvByFeatureReportRule
    A wrapper object for each rule returned in a User Report.
    IMkvByFeatureUserReport
    A wrapper object for the user-specific ByFeature Report.
    IMkvESDataAdapter  
    IMkvESDataProcessor  
    IMkvESLibStatusListener
    IMkvESLibStatusListener can be used to get notification about the availability and readiness of the Entitlement API engine.
    IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener
    IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener can be used to get notification about the availability and readiness of the Entitlement Namespaces.
    IMkvESNamespaceAvailabilityListener.IMkvNamespace
    This class is not meant to be implemented by application code.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MkvBulkEntitlementQuery
    MkvBulkEntitlementQuery is the wrapper of a Bulk Entitlement Query currently ongoing in the system.
    MkvBulkEntitlementRequest
    MkvBulkEntitlementRequest represents a request for a Bulk Entitlement Query.
    MkvByFeatureReportQuery
    MkvByFeatureReportQuery wraps the request for a ByFeature Report.
    MkvEntitlementEngine  
    MkvEntitlementRules  
    MkvNamespace  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IMkvByFeatureReportRule.RulePermission
    Defines the permission of the Entitlement Rule.
    IMkvByFeatureReportRule.RuleType
    Defines the type of Entitlement Rule
    USER_RULE: this is a rule configured at User level GROUP_RULE: this is a rule configured at Group level PROFILE_RULE: this is a rule configured at Profile level
    IMkvESDataAdapter.ES_CHAINS  
    MkvBulkEntitlementResponse  
    MkvEntitlementEngine.MkvByFeatureReportResult  
    MkvEntitlementRules.Permission  
    MkvESLibStatus
    MkvESLibStatus wraps the status of the underlying Entitlement API.
